        <p>Food insecurity is the lack of consistent access to enough food for an active, healthy life. It can affect anyone, regardless of their background or circumstances.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>Key Facts</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Millions of people worldwide face food insecurity daily</li>
            <li>Food insecurity can lead to serious health problems</li>
            <li>Children are particularly vulnerable to the effects of food insecurity</li>
            <li>Food insecurity can affect mental and physical development</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
